DataElement.preferredName: Clinical Trial Participant Prior Condition Other java.lang.String
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A research study that prospectively assigns human participants or groups of humans to one or more health-related interventions to evaluate the effects on health outcomes. Interventions include but are not restricted to drugs, cells and other biological products, surgical procedures, radiologic procedures, devices, behavioral treatments, process-of-care changes, and preventive care.:Someone who takes part in an activity.:Earlier in time or order.:A state of being, such as a state of health._Not otherwise specified._Generic value domain for a java datatype that is a class that represents character strings.
